    "Instructions": "To enable Google OAuth login:",
    "Step1": "1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/",
    "Step2": "2. Create a new project or select existing one",
    "Step3": "3. Enable Google+ API",
    "Step4": "4. Go to Credentials > Create Credentials > OAuth 2.0 Client ID",
    "Step5": "5. Set Application type to 'Web application'",
    "Step6": "6. Add Authorized redirect URIs: http://localhost:5234/Account/GoogleCallback (for development)",
    "Step7": "7. Copy Client ID and Client Secret to the fields above"
